text: Kozmodemyansk () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Kozmodemyanskoye Rural Settlement, Karagaysky District, Perm Krai, Russia. The population was 602 as of 2010. There are 15 streets. == Geography == It is located on the Yazva River. == References == Category:Rural localities in Karagaysky District
title: Kozmodemyansk, Perm Krai
